{"tid":1912187,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Naughty Dog宣布將與HBO合作推出《The Last of Us》電視劇","createTime":"2020-03-06T01:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T09:29:18.000Z","uid":75050,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4dbeef7e0a9c39b5714f527b51cd88e017fe5e","tid":1912187,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GLXUnHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGLXUnHA.jpg&h=2a30cb82&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNaughty Dog宣布將與HBO合作推出《The Last of Us》電視劇，Naughty Dog創意總監Neil Druckmann和美劇《Chernobyl》編劇Craig Mazin將共同擔任導演和編劇。曾創作《The Sopranos》《Sex and the City》等劇的Carolyn Strauss和Naughty Dog總裁Evan Wells也將出任本劇的執行制作人。<br />\n<br />\n這將是PlayStation Productions推出的第一部電視劇，主要呈現《The Last of Us 1》的故事，但也有可能加入《The Last of Us 二部曲》的相關內容。IGN表示本劇將取代之前的《The Last of Us》電影項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEqVRAW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEqVRAW.jpg&h=075070d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67f4b49736dc829379cc960acc6ed910dfbf9b7f","tid":1912187,"uid":3172,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g35R9o7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg35R9o7.jpg&h=327188c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nellen page 做？"},{"pid":"9963433675155d7278a9e0ec2f8ae9cfb7c1ab34","tid":1912187,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f4b49736dc829379cc960acc6ed910dfbf9b7f","tid":1912187,"uid":3172,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g35R9o7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg35R9o7.jpg&h=327188c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nellen page 做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"老左好多了"},{"pid":"b9794289c8eddc25d2181bbd773c5975